== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Valentine Uwamariya yavutse ku ya 14 Gicurasi 1971 mu Murenge wa Shangi [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|mu Karere]] ka [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Nyamasheke]]. Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'amashuri yisumbuye muri Groupe Scolaire Sainte Famille, [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Nyamasheke]]. Yakomeje amashuri ye kandi abona impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Chimie Organic yakuye muri [[kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda]]. Mu 2005, Uwamariya yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Electrochemistry yakuye muri kaminuza ya Witwatersrand muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Nyuma yaho, 2007, yabonye buruse yo kwiga Porogaramu ya PhD muri UNESCO-IHE naho muri 2013 abona impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga. <ref name=":04">{{Cite news|title=Dr. Valentine UWAMARIYA {{!}} The Minister of Education|url=https://www.mineduc.gov.rw/about}}</ref> <ref name=":22">{{Cite web|date=2020-02-27|title=Meet The New Cabinet Members|url=https://www.ktpress.rw/2020/02/meet-the-new-cabinet-members/|access-date=2021-09-17|website=KT PRESS|language=en-US}}</ref> <ref name=":23">{{Cite web|date=2020-02-27|title=Meet The New Cabinet Members|url=https://www.ktpress.rw/2020/02/meet-the-new-cabinet-members/|access-date=2021-09-17|website=KT PRESS|language=en-US}}</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Uwamariya yabaye umuyobozi wungirije wungirije ushinzwe amahugurwa, iterambere ry’ibigo n’ubushakashatsi muri Rwanda Polytechnic iherutse gushingwa mbere gato yuko aba Minisitiri w’uburezi. <ref name=":05">{{Cite news|title=Dr. Valentine UWAMARIYA {{!}} The Minister of Education|url=https://www.mineduc.gov.rw/about}}</ref> <ref name=":24">{{Cite web|date=2020-02-27|title=Meet The New Cabinet Members|url=https://www.ktpress.rw/2020/02/meet-the-new-cabinet-members/|access-date=2021-09-17|website=KT PRESS|language=en-US}}</ref>

